- How about those big brown eyes?
- No, they're blue.

356
00:22:42,069 --> 00:22:43,069
Brown.

357
00:22:44,113 --> 00:22:45,780
Uh... Blue.

358
00:22:48,868 --> 00:22:51,453
Oh. Yeah, deep blue.

359
