- Yes, sir!
- [Waverly chuckles]

1387
01:28:15,415 --> 01:28:17,208
Now, that didn't hurt too much, did it?

1388
01:28:17,376 --> 01:28:20,962
You know, in some ways, you're
far superior to my cocker spaniel.

1389
